Package: commerce
Title: Department of Commerce Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the U.S. Department of Commerce open data endpoints.
    Provides access to the Enterprise Data Inventory (1964 datasets), CIO governance
    boards, IT cost savings strategies, and bureau IT leadership directory.
